item.title: CVE-2019-1010308|2024-08-05T03:07:18.494Z -- aquaverde%20gmbh -- aquarius%20cms
item.description: Aquaverde GmbH Aquarius CMS prior to version 4.1.1 is affected by: Incorrect Access Control. The impact is: The access to the log file is not restricted. It contains sensitive information like passwords etc. The component is: log file. The attack vector is: open the file.
